      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Ok...figured out... The API is returning a vector of size two, and the values are two String arrays. Those String arrays are expected to contain values, and in this case for some reason, was empty. Thats a problem with the api call only. But as you all said, the cast exception was due to the String[] and String. Thanks for all the help!"
